_json.description: In the last 60 years Bunny Rabbits have been increasingly kept as pets in the UK & other countries. In ten years there has been an big increase in the UK making them the nation's third most popular furry pet. In 2010, 1 million rabbits were kept as pets. Before taking on the commitment of caring for a rabbit consideration should be given to whether its physical & emotional needs can be met. Properly caring for a rabbit can take significant time & cost #ThinkCareFully
